{"word":"κατακρημνίζω","slug":"κατακρημνίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατακρημνίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to throw down a precipice</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>generally, <i>to throw headlong down</i>, <el>ἐκ τριηρέων</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be so thrown down</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}